# Introduction
Hello, I'm Petro! üëã 

I am a Product Engineer with strong focus on backend and I currently live in [Myrhorod, Ukraine](https://goo.gl/maps/J2bcjYx8VnM63ZfeA?coh=178571&entry=tt). This README should help you learn about me and the ways I work and how best to work with me. Feel free to chat with me about `#workwarbalance`, `#neurodiversity`, `#playbacktheatre`, `#predictability`, and `#radicaltransparency`

# Background

Git, Ruby, and RSpec have been my main tools since my career began. During the weekends, I'm [performing in the playback theatre](https://dou.ua/lenta/articles/dou-hobby-playback/) in Kyiv and [other cities of Ukraine](https://www.facebook.com/MalePlaybackUA). I've worked with [kottans.org community](https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLEK9H5bICxvoiDKQ7epRpxUDmQotmvsgM) in the past. I'm a passionate practitioner of ["Go Scrum Yourself"(c)(tm) framework](https://goscrumyourself.carrd.co/), UPMA‚ìá and of [ALKOframework](https://gitlab.com/nowhere-inc/tech-ninjas/alkoframework). My favorite sport is squash: commit squashing. [Feel free to schedule some talk with me](https://calendly.com/petrokoriakin/talk-to-petro?month=2023-03)

# How to collaborate with Petro

I'm a feedback-driven and context-addicted personality. I write a lot to make sure no essential details are missed. When working on a project, my creativity and ability to find **smart workarounds** followed by **boring solutions** can propel it the most. On the other hand, I dislike my unconscious focus on ü§ùcollaboration and üëÅÔ∏ètransparency instead of  üìàresults and ‚è±Ô∏èefficiency. I welcome direct, actionable feedback from customers, co-workers, code review comments, and even RSpec telling me the specs are failing. Here is the anonymous form, and I encourage you to write down some words about our cooperation https://forms.gle/j9dPdXYgV4qe4o246 

